<p>Webform is relied upon for everything from contact forms, to donations to event registrations.</p>
<p>By default, Webform sends emails in plain text. In this tutorial, we're going to show you how to send Webform emails in plain text, which allows you choose different layouts or designs.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ostrainingdrupal/~4/YkQ8HQFrl2k" height="1" width="1"/>
